dct_title_s: Chart of part of the Bahama Islands showing the tracks ascribed to Columbus on his discovery of the New World
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Depths shown by soundings.
compiled and drawn, under the direction of W.T. Bright, in charge of Drawing Division, U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey Office ; by T.J. O'Sullivan, draughtsman.
